title: The Cosy Club
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A homey decor and the eating area is dimly lift for atmosphere. Ask for the separate vegan menu which includes several brunch (until 6pm) and starters as well as 2 mains and 2 sandwiches (until 6pm). Kitchen stops at 10m. There are stairs from the entrance to the eating area but there is a wheelchair lift for disabled access.
